A given modality of interaction has certain capabilities.

"logging in from a net cafe is different than logging in from your 
 home office is different than logging in from your phone"


    
    Capabilities 
        What resources do you have right now

        * Phone
        * Internet access
        * At least 2 hours of free time
        * Brainpower
        * _No_ brainpower
        * Color printer
        * Fax
        * Whiteboard
        * Grocery store
        * Business Hours



